snippet: At least seven people died after a wooden boat collided with a Greek Coast Guard vessel off the Greek island of Lesbos, according to an official, who added that the cause of the incident was being investigated.
abstract: Wooden boat collides with Greek Coast Guard rescue vessel in Aegean Sea, killing seven refugees.
lead_paragraph: At least seven people died after a wooden boat collided with a Greek Coast Guard vessel off the Greek island of Lesbos, according to an official, who added that the cause of the incident was being investigated.
